00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC for SHIB/USDT perpetuals. The rate is determined by the premium between perpetual price and spot index, with additional interest rate component typically set at 0.01% per interval. When funding is positive, long positions pay shorts; when negative, shorts pay longs. Payment occurs automatically at funding timestamps for open positions."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
